noted.', 'Synergism, Excretion', 'If possible, drugs that are potentially nephrotoxic including NSAIDs should be avoided during the 5 days of clofarabine administration.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/69999/', '', 'Mercaptopurine, Cladribine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Nelarabine, Cytarabine, Fludarabine, Decitabine, Azacitidine, Capecitabine', 'Rabeprazole, Misoprostol, Chondroitin sulfate, Glucosamine, Esomeprazole', 1767369485);
