armacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/70035/', '', 'Fluorouracil, Pemetrexed, Mercaptopurine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Gemcitabine, Nelarabine, Cytarabine, Pralatrexate, Fludarabine, Decitabine, More', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Amivantamab, More', 1767369485);
