mic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/70087/', '', 'Brivaracetam, Topiramate, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Lamotrigine, Methylphenobarbital, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, Oxcarbazepine, More', 'Pemetrexed, Mercaptopurine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Gemcitabine, Nelarabine, Cytarabine, Pralatrexate, Fludarabine, Decitabine, Azacitidine', 1767369485);
